{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2300109, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 441704, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "何不直接overleaf", "timestamp": 1629207713, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300114, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 441704, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不用，Markdown挺好的", "timestamp": 1629207787, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300133, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 441704, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "vscode配\nLatex Workshop插件比较好", "timestamp": 1629207931, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300138, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441704, "reply_to": 2300109, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: overleaf团队协作挺好，但是dz想使用本地的软件，overleaf在一些deadline附近经常掉线", "timestamp": 1629208020, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300141, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441704, "reply_to": 2300114, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 主要写paper用，md排版不如tex", "timestamp": 1629208069, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300144, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441704, "reply_to": 2300133, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 以前也听人推荐过，但感觉插件终归还是没有专门的软件强大", "timestamp": 1629208162, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300172, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 441704, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "只用过后两个，texpad可以实时显示（吹爆，就是中文的实时显示要到网上搜一下配置）而且界面更好看些", "timestamp": 1629208524, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300178, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 441704, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当然还有就是texpad正版有点贵可以试着找找资源", "timestamp": 1629208579, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300204, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 441704, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "texpad胜在实时编译（开启live模式），也就是左边编辑着，右边就有实时的pdf更新，但个人体验，在有些时候，如果用pdflatex或者图比较多的时候，就会有点卡（其实究竟是哪个原因没有去细究过），例如做beamer的时候live模式可能比较卡。除此之外，texpad几乎完全不需要个人配置什么东西吧，跟overleaf差不多，随手就用，（缺点就是收费），所以texpad一般用来处理一些小的工程或者图较少的。cz常用的是，用sublime text作为编辑器，然后在sublime text里绑定skim作为pdf的浏览器，这样也相当方便。具体配置方案，关键词“sublime latex skim配置”", "timestamp": 1629208855, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300235, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 441704, "reply_to": 2300204, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 好像用pdflatex的时候不能实时显示了，只有用texpadtex才可以实时显示，所以如果追求实时显示的话蛮多包用不了，比如ctex就用不了", "timestamp": 1629209234, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300309, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 441704, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "vscode", "timestamp": 1629209979, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300354, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441704, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "感谢dave和eve", "timestamp": 1629210399, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300389, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 441704, "reply_to": 2300138, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 在自己服务器上用docker开一个overleaf，感觉体验很好😂", "timestamp": 1629210712, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2301189, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441704, "reply_to": 2300389, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 有点geek的感觉😃", "timestamp": 1629216356, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 9, "pid": 441704, "reply": 14, "tag": null, "text": "洞友推荐下Mac-pro的latex软件，说说亲用体验", "timestamp": 1629207594, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629216355, "url": "", "vote": {"vote_data": {"MacTex": 8, "Texpad": 5, "Texstudio": 8}, "vote_options": ["MacTex", "Texpad", "Texstudio"]}}}